<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=ef5e6f3e3e0fa221de70a8b865db65ae sig_cn_org=4a9e339b4f9de5c9c9362e3a7f7d9b7f source=18.3 
     <para>
      For example, an error report about mismatched timeline number in a
      backup manifest showed the starting timeline number where it meant
      to show the ending timeline number.
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      例如，关于备份清单中时间线编号不匹配的错误报告
      显示了起始时间线编号，而应该显示结束时间线编号。
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=ef5e6f3e3e0fa221de70a8b865db65ae -->
    </listitem>

