Branch: master [45d92b76d] 2025-12-29 15:47:31 +1300
Branch: REL_18_STABLE [4da5c33a3] 2025-12-29 15:48:27 +1300
Branch: REL_17_STABLE [b3c8119e2] 2025-12-29 15:28:17 +1300
Branch: REL_16_STABLE [80e8ec772] 2025-12-29 15:31:39 +1300
-->
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=83b9bb81a89d973052c30ea2106c6d48 sig_cn_org=8876726de43d5b9e043e7be39d285e24 source=18.3 
     <para>
      Honor <function>open()</function>'s <literal>O_CLOEXEC</literal>
      flag on Windows (Bryan Green, Thomas Munro)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;bebb281b0">&sect;</ulink>
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;a7d06e74d">&sect;</ulink>
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;4da5c33a3">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      在 Windows 上支持 <function>open()</function> 的 <literal>O_CLOEXEC</literal>
      标志 (Bryan Green, Thomas Munro)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;bebb281b0">&sect;</ulink>
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;a7d06e74d">&sect;</ulink>
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;4da5c33a3">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=83b9bb81a89d973052c30ea2106c6d48 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=a2668528735e08177ac2eef740c37f5e sig_cn_org=653fd344eabd3d70f7d288a895031047 source=18.3 
     <para>
      Make this flag work like it does on POSIX platforms, so that we
      don't leak file handles into child processes such as <literal>COPY
      TO/FROM PROGRAM</literal>.  While that leakage hasn't caused many
      problems, it seems undesirable.
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      使这个标志在 POSIX 平台上工作，以便我们
      不会将文件句柄泄漏到子进程中，例如 <literal>COPY
      TO/FROM PROGRAM</literal>。虽然这种泄漏并没有造成太多
      问题，但似乎并不理想。
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=a2668528735e08177ac2eef740c37f5e -->
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
