<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=07c1bb458489f67f424a76d0f8201c51 sig_cn_org=6ae58fd2481515059e55a4939d41df93 source=18.3 
     <para>
      Ensure that BRIN autosummarization provides a snapshot for index
      expressions that need one (Álvaro Herrera)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;419ffde23">&sect;</ulink>
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;8733f0b54">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      确保 BRIN 自动汇总为需要快照的索引表达式提供快照
      （Álvaro Herrera）
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;419ffde23">&sect;</ulink>
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;8733f0b54">&sect;</ulink>
</para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=07c1bb458489f67f424a76d0f8201c51 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=cf9dbc230d2b4f658426c325ae4e5f6e sig_cn_org=cefc57a442d9dc2bc004769730ba4646 source=18.3 
     <para>
      Previously, autosummarization would fail for such indexes, and then
      leave placeholder index tuples behind, causing the index to bloat
      over time.
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      之前，自动汇总会在这些索引上失败，然后留下占位符索引元组，导致索引随着时间的推移而膨胀。
</para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=cf9dbc230d2b4f658426c325ae4e5f6e -->
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--
Author: David Rowley <drowley@postgresql.org>
