<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=7fcc1b0cdcf945b0a02c47db6855e64e sig_cn_org=3c3b07d0c2830b27ed657b3f83a498eb source=18.3 
     <para>
      Fix <function>pg_restore_relation_stats()</function>,
      <function>pg_clear_relation_stats()</function>,
      <function>pg_restore_attribute_stats()</function>, and
      <function>pg_clear_attribute_stats()</function> to check
      privileges before acquiring lock on the target relation
      rather than after.
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      修复 <function>pg_restore_relation_stats()</function>,
      <function>pg_clear_relation_stats()</function>,
      <function>pg_restore_attribute_stats()</function> 和
      <function>pg_clear_attribute_stats()</function> 在获取目标关系的锁之前检查
      权限，而不是之后。
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=7fcc1b0cdcf945b0a02c47db6855e64e -->
    </listitem>

