-->
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=2836987b664fb90cb6d8a6206fe5a345 sig_cn_org=193083cf3d3e9da9a85e39c0274cabcb source=18.3 
     <para>
      Fix incorrect reporting of replication lag
      in <structname>pg_stat_replication</structname> view (Fujii Masao)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;9670032cc">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      修复 <structname>pg_stat_replication</structname> 视图中复制延迟的错误报告
      （Fujii Masao）
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;9670032cc">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=2836987b664fb90cb6d8a6206fe5a345 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=11a8fc0e77bce9700f47c69e74143bc7 sig_cn_org=aec6c48ccddefb79061683b50f1a3998 source=18.3 
     <para>
      If any standby server's replay LSN stopped advancing,
      the <structfield>write_lag</structfield>
      and <structfield>flush_lag</structfield> columns would eventually
      stop updating.
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      如果任何备用服务器的重放 LSN 停止前进，
      <structfield>write_lag</structfield>
      和 <structfield>flush_lag</structfield> 列最终将停止更新。
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=11a8fc0e77bce9700f47c69e74143bc7 -->
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
