<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=e9596e043520f7cb0c27ad0033a90443 sig_cn_org=cff91b2fba36fe3dffda77ad302fbd98 source=18.3 
     <para>
      Correctly handle <literal>GROUP BY DISTINCT</literal> in PL/pgSQL
      assignment statements (Tom Lane)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;78a284b0b">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      正确处理 PL/pgSQL 赋值语句中的 <literal>GROUP BY DISTINCT</literal>
      （Tom Lane）
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;78a284b0b">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=e9596e043520f7cb0c27ad0033a90443 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=3064f0897ade8ef7c811ef6f40364e79 sig_cn_org=fe1b3973408a894e010c2b9d297a81a6 source=18.3 
     <para>
      The parser failed to record the <literal>DISTINCT</literal> option
      in this context, so that the command would act as if it were
      plain <literal>GROUP BY</literal>.
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      解析器未能在此上下文中记录 <literal>DISTINCT</literal> 选项，
      以至于该命令的行为就像是普通的 <literal>GROUP BY</literal>。
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=3064f0897ade8ef7c811ef6f40364e79 -->
    </listitem>

