<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=24a585e7b427a577a3d3e6a7773ff89b sig_cn_org=bc763dadce9e8b8b8b122106ad653769 source=18.3 
     <para>
      In <application>pgbench</application>, fix faulty assertion about
      errors in pipeline mode (Yugo Nagata)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;c736808e0">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      在 <application>pgbench</application> 中，修复关于管道模式
      中错误的断言 (Yugo Nagata)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;c736808e0">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=24a585e7b427a577a3d3e6a7773ff89b -->
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
