    <sect4 id="release-18-server-config">
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=c311faa4db812ea8d68b8f9701081a79 sig_cn_org=None source=14.1 
     <title>Server Configuration</title>
________________________________________________________-->
     <title>服务器配置</title>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=c311faa4db812ea8d68b8f9701081a79 -->

     <itemizedlist>

<!--
Author: Daniel Gustafsson <dgustafsson@postgresql.org>
2025-02-20 [b3f0be788] Add support for OAUTHBEARER SASL mechanism
-->

      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=ef2703710a73361afbab3a5fc3664148 sig_cn_org=a6731006e75e612ec0d6379772c1f4cf source=18.3 
      <para>
      Add support for the <link linkend="auth-oauth">OAuth authentication
      method</link> (Jacob Champion, Daniel Gustafsson, Thomas Munro)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;b3f0be788">&sect;</ulink>
      </para>
________________________________________________________-->
      <para>
      添加对 <link linkend="auth-oauth">OAuth 认证方法</link> 的支持
      (Jacob Champion, Daniel Gustafsson, Thomas Munro)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;b3f0be788">&sect;</ulink>
      </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=ef2703710a73361afbab3a5fc3664148 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=3a2ad6c43f6ffbea99ffa4a5eab23ebb sig_cn_org=b0ad60facbdab3e00c9ce1d1ac7ac65f source=18.3 
      <para>
      This adds an <literal>oauth</literal> authentication method to <link
      linkend="auth-pg-hba-conf"><filename>pg_hba.conf</filename></link>,
      libpq OAuth options, a server variable <xref
      linkend="guc-oauth-validator-libraries"/> to load
      token validation libraries, and a configure flag <link
      linkend="configure-option-with-libcurl"><option>-&minus;with-libcurl</option></link>
      to add the required compile-time libraries.
      </para>
________________________________________________________-->
      <para>
      这为 <link linkend="auth-pg-hba-conf"><filename>pg_hba.conf</filename></link>
      添加了一个 <literal>oauth</literal> 认证方法，libpq OAuth 选项，一个服务器变量 <xref
      linkend="guc-oauth-validator-libraries"/> 用于加载
      令牌验证库，以及一个配置标志 <link
      linkend="configure-option-with-libcurl"><option>--with-libcurl</option></link>
      用于添加所需的编译时库。
      </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=3a2ad6c43f6ffbea99ffa4a5eab23ebb -->
      </listitem>

<!--
Author: Daniel Gustafsson <dgustafsson@postgresql.org>
2024-10-24 [45188c2ea] Support configuring TLSv1.3 cipher suites
-->

      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=835d6410fdaa20e6adb3f60000125142 sig_cn_org=eb8504e4511c21241d20d921e9d9f093 source=18.3 
      <para>
      Add server variable <xref linkend="guc-ssl-tls13-ciphers"/> to allow
      specification of multiple colon-separated TLSv1.3 cipher suites
      (Erica Zhang, Daniel Gustafsson)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;45188c2ea">&sect;</ulink>
      </para>
________________________________________________________-->
      <para>
      添加服务器变量 <xref linkend="guc-ssl-tls13-ciphers"/> 以允许
      指定多个以冒号分隔的 TLSv1.3 密码套件
      (Erica Zhang, Daniel Gustafsson)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;45188c2ea">&sect;</ulink>
      </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=835d6410fdaa20e6adb3f60000125142 -->
      </listitem>

<!--
Author: Daniel Gustafsson <dgustafsson@postgresql.org>
2025-03-18 [daa02c6bd] Add X25519 to the default set of curves
-->

      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=75e72432702cc8feb27b380fa5a9664e sig_cn_org=cd374aa2ba3a4f429d41f4a6f520d4b8 source=18.3 
      <para>
      Change server variable <xref linkend="guc-ssl-groups"/>'s default
      to include elliptic curve X25519 (Daniel Gustafsson, Jacob Champion)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;daa02c6bd">&sect;</ulink>
      </para>
________________________________________________________-->
      <para>
      更改服务器变量 <xref linkend="guc-ssl-groups"/> 的默认值
      以包括椭圆曲线 X25519 (Daniel Gustafsson, Jacob Champion)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;daa02c6bd">&sect;</ulink>
      </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=75e72432702cc8feb27b380fa5a9664e -->
      </listitem>

<!--
Author: Daniel Gustafsson <dgustafsson@postgresql.org>
2024-10-24 [3d1ef3a15] Support configuring multiple ECDH curves
-->

      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=faadb24228bf2e58e14d6798dea09b97 sig_cn_org=eaa4e57def0def3524aecce6f61db863 source=18.3 
      <para>
      Rename server variable <varname>ssl_ecdh_curve</varname> to <xref
      linkend="guc-ssl-groups"/> and allow multiple colon-separated
      <acronym>ECDH</acronym> curves to be specified (Erica Zhang,
      Daniel Gustafsson)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;3d1ef3a15">&sect;</ulink>
      </para>
________________________________________________________-->
      <para>
      将服务器变量 <varname>ssl_ecdh_curve</varname> 重命名为 <xref
      linkend="guc-ssl-groups"/> 并允许指定多个以冒号分隔的
      <acronym>ECDH</acronym> 曲线 (Erica Zhang,
      Daniel Gustafsson)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;3d1ef3a15">&sect;</ulink>
      </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=faadb24228bf2e58e14d6798dea09b97 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=1091b8cb7a7a156faf9950ea789ec186 sig_cn_org=2e949e4d72831bba41bf8b11c17db979 source=18.3 
      <para>
      The previous name still works.
      </para>
________________________________________________________-->
      <para>
      之前的名称仍然有效。
      </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=1091b8cb7a7a156faf9950ea789ec186 -->
      </listitem>

<!--
Author: Heikki Linnakangas <heikki.linnakangas@iki.fi>
2025-04-02 [a460251f0] Make cancel request keys longer
Author: Heikki Linnakangas <heikki.linnakangas@iki.fi>
2024-07-29 [9d9b9d46f] Move cancel key generation to after forking the backend
-->

      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=5bf099b19b95a656b0386c3a9d5797ee sig_cn_org=4a7908e5276f5240577a8dd3d0595f1a source=18.3 
      <para>
      Make <link linkend="functions-admin-signal-table">cancel request
      keys</link> 256 bits (Heikki Linnakangas, Jelte Fennema-Nio)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;a460251f0">&sect;</ulink>
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;9d9b9d46f">&sect;</ulink>
      </para>
________________________________________________________-->
      <para>
      将 <link linkend="functions-admin-signal-table">取消请求键</link> 设置为 256 位
      (Heikki Linnakangas, Jelte Fennema-Nio)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;a460251f0">&sect;</ulink>
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;9d9b9d46f">&sect;</ulink>
      </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=5bf099b19b95a656b0386c3a9d5797ee -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=6fc6fb90bfe5b7d7949ca221f6418ed4 sig_cn_org=4af3d715457845ad23a635dd1febf4b4 source=18.3 
      <para>
      This is only possible when the server and client support wire
      protocol version 3.2, introduced in this release.
      </para>
________________________________________________________-->
      <para>
      这只有在服务器和客户端支持在此版本中引入的
      3.2 版本的 wire 协议时才可能。
      </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=6fc6fb90bfe5b7d7949ca221f6418ed4 -->
      </listitem>

<!--
Author: Nathan Bossart <nathan@postgresql.org>
2025-01-06 [c758119e5] Allow changing autovacuum_max_workers without restarting
-->

      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=801fdf1822027d794320900e67f975e2 sig_cn_org=f91df4e91fab78854e1646546717762e source=18.3 
      <para>
      Add server variable <xref linkend="guc-autovacuum-worker-slots"/>
      to specify the maximum number of background workers (Nathan Bossart)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;c758119e5">&sect;</ulink>
      </para>
________________________________________________________-->
      <para>
      添加服务器变量 <xref linkend="guc-autovacuum-worker-slots"/>
      以指定最大后台工作进程数量 (Nathan Bossart)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;c758119e5">&sect;</ulink>
      </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=801fdf1822027d794320900e67f975e2 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=a26cd5e1d996fbb8459ead6d14e20335 sig_cn_org=9b046f1aae2de6ae4b88413a0d55780c source=18.3 
      <para>
      With this variable set, <xref linkend="guc-autovacuum-max-workers"/>
      can be adjusted at runtime up to this maximum without a server
      restart.
      </para>
________________________________________________________-->
      <para>
      设置此变量后，<xref linkend="guc-autovacuum-max-workers"/>
      可以在运行时调整到此最大值，而无需重启服务器。
      </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=a26cd5e1d996fbb8459ead6d14e20335 -->
      </listitem>

<!--
Author: Nathan Bossart <nathan@postgresql.org>
2025-02-05 [306dc520b] Introduce autovacuum_vacuum_max_threshold.
-->

      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=1b6875de08e4e7943c5781488d2caa0e sig_cn_org=ae0623da36ef2860eef4557688fdac18 source=18.3 
      <para>
      Allow specification of the fixed number of dead tuples that will
      trigger an <link linkend="autovacuum">autovacuum</link> (Nathan
      Bossart, Frédéric Yhuel)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;306dc520b">&sect;</ulink>
      </para>
________________________________________________________-->
      <para>
      允许指定固定数量的死元组，以触发一个 <link linkend="autovacuum">autovacuum</link>
      (Nathan Bossart, Frédéric Yhuel)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;306dc520b">&sect;</ulink>
      </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=1b6875de08e4e7943c5781488d2caa0e -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=b3d04d5e56cf00d5e5c9dabb1008413f sig_cn_org=a65f54c385227b8fb1dac461cd8a9e15 source=18.3 
      <para>
      The server variable is <xref
      linkend="guc-autovacuum-vacuum-max-threshold"/>.  Percentages are
      still used for triggering.
      </para>
________________________________________________________-->
      <para>
      服务器变量是 <xref
      linkend="guc-autovacuum-vacuum-max-threshold"/>。百分比仍然用于触发。
      </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=b3d04d5e56cf00d5e5c9dabb1008413f -->
      </listitem>

<!--
Author: Andres Freund <andres@anarazel.de>
2025-03-24 [adb5f85fa] Redefine max_files_per_process to control additionally o
-->

      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=9e1775fa1dfcadffb8e45d21b7dadcc5 sig_cn_org=3113c881fccdc920f92a6a2cff0acb08 source=18.3 
      <para>
      Change server variable <xref linkend="guc-max-files-per-process"/>
      to limit only files opened by a backend (Andres Freund)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;adb5f85fa">&sect;</ulink>
      </para>
________________________________________________________-->
