<!--
Author: Jeff Davis <jdavis@postgresql.org>
2025-01-17 [d3d098316] Support PG_UNICODE_FAST locale in the builtin collation
-->

     <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=9c10188caab169bd6d0c36f534567593 sig_cn_org=33b8ba2d896624360a578a7c581acd4a source=18.3 
     <para>
     Add builtin collation provider <link
     linkend="locale-providers"><literal>PG_UNICODE_FAST</literal></link>
     (Jeff Davis)
     <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;d3d098316">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
     添加内置排序提供者 <link linkend="locale-providers"><literal>PG_UNICODE_FAST</literal></link>（Jeff Davis）
     <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;d3d098316">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=9c10188caab169bd6d0c36f534567593 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=dc42990eaf16ea9da6445a6e2faa4808 sig_cn_org=99b25389b58c71f1c8d0e827348430ee source=18.3 
     <para>
     This locale supports case mapping, but sorts in code point order,
     not natural language order.
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
     此区域设置支持大小写映射，但按代码点顺序排序，而不是自然语言顺序。
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=dc42990eaf16ea9da6445a6e2faa4808 -->
     </listitem>

<!--
Author: David Rowley <drowley@postgresql.org>
2024-09-24 [62ddf7ee9] Add ONLY support for VACUUM and ANALYZE
-->

     <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=4bcb5503ed04ec983f5bb828485b77b4 sig_cn_org=724660cbe468fb2fd86c9f80ab91f866 source=18.3 
     <para>
     Allow <xref linkend="sql-vacuum"/> and <xref linkend="sql-analyze"/>
     to process partitioned tables without processing their children
     (Michael Harris)
     <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;62ddf7ee9">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
     允许 <xref linkend="sql-vacuum"/> 和 <xref linkend="sql-analyze"/> 处理分区表而不处理其子表（Michael Harris）
     <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;62ddf7ee9">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=4bcb5503ed04ec983f5bb828485b77b4 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=6eaa66f81ee5d5488c6e31ced9b693c4 sig_cn_org=11615d02bf95480a06349b205e3811c5 source=18.3 
     <para>
     This is enabled with the new <literal>ONLY</literal> option.  This is
     useful since autovacuum does not process partitioned tables, just
     its children.
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
     这可以通过新的 <literal>ONLY</literal> 选项启用。这是有用的，因为 autovacuum 不处理分区表，只处理其子表。
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=6eaa66f81ee5d5488c6e31ced9b693c4 -->
     </listitem>

<!--
Author: Jeff Davis <jdavis@postgresql.org>
2024-10-11 [e839c8ecc] Create functions pg_set_relation_stats, pg_clear_relatio
Author: Jeff Davis <jdavis@postgresql.org>
2024-10-24 [d32d14639] Add functions pg_restore_relation_stats(), pg_restore_at
Author: Jeff Davis <jdavis@postgresql.org>
2025-03-25 [650ab8aaf] Stats: use schemaname/relname instead of regclass.
-->

     <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=90a9608450511128b236f414bcb78831 sig_cn_org=16664e275e07c05464492be11eaeec61 source=18.3 
     <para>
     Add functions to modify per-relation and per-column optimizer
     statistics (Corey Huinker)
     <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;e839c8ecc">&sect;</ulink>
     <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;d32d14639">&sect;</ulink>
     <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;650ab8aaf">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
     添加函数以修改每个关系和每列的优化器统计信息（Corey Huinker）
     <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;e839c8ecc">&sect;</ulink>
     <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;d32d14639">&sect;</ulink>
     <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;650ab8aaf">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=90a9608450511128b236f414bcb78831 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=beb140188e8f4b71e66fd0e7cd14602f sig_cn_org=3aaa6dafd5d3baca3037c684c5116c09 source=18.3 
     <para>
     The functions are <link
     linkend="functions-admin-statsmod"><function>pg_restore_relation_stats()</function></link>,
     <function>pg_restore_attribute_stats()</function>,
     <function>pg_clear_relation_stats()</function>, and
     <function>pg_clear_attribute_stats()</function>.
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
     这些函数是 <link linkend="functions-admin-statsmod"><function>pg_restore_relation_stats()</function></link>、<function>pg_restore_attribute_stats()</function>、<function>pg_clear_relation_stats()</function> 和 <function>pg_clear_attribute_stats()</function>。
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=beb140188e8f4b71e66fd0e7cd14602f -->
     </listitem>


<!--
Author: Thomas Munro <tmunro@postgresql.org>
2025-04-08 [f78ca6f3e] Introduce file_copy_method setting.
-->

     <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=13ad51c19ca22e615112d777bb54b6d5 sig_cn_org=0f10429aa5105b1eb4fa3371a3c1ca0d source=18.3 
     <para>
     Add server variable <xref linkend="guc-file-copy-method"/> to control
     the file copying method (Nazir Bilal Yavuz)
     <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;f78ca6f3e">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
     添加服务器变量 <xref linkend="guc-file-copy-method"/> 以控制
     文件复制方法 (Nazir Bilal Yavuz)
     <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;f78ca6f3e">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=13ad51c19ca22e615112d777bb54b6d5 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=0f0a829f5267af807bf0e3de35b23000 sig_cn_org=a70b4e966dd3261e16bbd5c22fc73b1d source=18.3 
     <para>
     This controls whether <link
     linkend="sql-createdatabase"><command>CREATE DATABASE
     ... STRATEGY=FILE_COPY</command></link> and <link
     linkend="sql-alterdatabase"><command>ALTER DATABASE ... SET
     TABLESPACE</command></link> uses file copy or clone.
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
     这控制 <link
     linkend="sql-createdatabase"><command>CREATE DATABASE
     ... STRATEGY=FILE_COPY</command></link> 和 <link
     linkend="sql-alterdatabase"><command>ALTER DATABASE ... SET
     TABLESPACE</command></link> 是否使用文件复制或克隆。
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=0f0a829f5267af807bf0e3de35b23000 -->
     </listitem>

    </itemizedlist>

    <sect4 id="release-18-constraints">
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=e87e2d762b22b6025172de72e816e0eb sig_cn_org=04bd75926faf5947b0996bceeb85c4d5 source=18.3 
     <title><link linkend="ddl-constraints">Constraints</link></title>
________________________________________________________-->
     <title><link linkend="ddl-constraints">约束</link></title>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=e87e2d762b22b6025172de72e816e0eb -->

     <itemizedlist>

<!--
Author: Peter Eisentraut <peter@eisentraut.org>
2024-09-17 [fc0438b4e] Add temporal PRIMARY KEY and UNIQUE constraints
Author: Peter Eisentraut <peter@eisentraut.org>
2024-09-17 [89f908a6d] Add temporal FOREIGN KEY contraints
-->

      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=8ff512b7ddee3f823bb7881ddeb24e26 sig_cn_org=bb6a77ac51bafe241cc7be675ac83234 source=18.3 
      <para>
      Allow the specification of non-overlapping <link
      linkend="sql-createtable-parms-primary-key"><literal>PRIMARY
      KEY</literal></link>, <link linkend="sql-createtable-parms-unique">
      <literal>UNIQUE</literal></link>, and
      <link linkend="sql-createtable-parms-references">foreign key</link>
      constraints (Paul A. Jungwirth)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;fc0438b4e">&sect;</ulink>
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;89f908a6d">&sect;</ulink>
      </para>
________________________________________________________-->
      <para>
      允许指定不重叠的 <link
      linkend="sql-createtable-parms-primary-key"><literal>主键</literal></link>、<link linkend="sql-createtable-parms-unique">
      <literal>唯一</literal></link> 和
      <link linkend="sql-createtable-parms-references">外键</link>
      约束 (Paul A. Jungwirth)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;fc0438b4e">&sect;</ulink>
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;89f908a6d">&sect;</ulink>
      </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=8ff512b7ddee3f823bb7881ddeb24e26 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=3d22087f1026ea5baa71f49f4cca45d6 sig_cn_org=f41250d43cf7b13067cc6eb38445badc source=18.3 
      <para>
      This is specified by <literal>WITHOUT OVERLAPS</literal> for
      <literal>PRIMARY KEY</literal> and <literal>UNIQUE</literal>, and by
      <literal>PERIOD</literal> for foreign keys, all applied to the last
      specified column.
      </para>
________________________________________________________-->
      <para>
      这通过 <literal>WITHOUT OVERLAPS</literal> 为
      <literal>PRIMARY KEY</literal> 和 <literal>UNIQUE</literal> 指定，通过
      <literal>PERIOD</literal> 为外键，均适用于最后指定的列。
      </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=3d22087f1026ea5baa71f49f4cca45d6 -->
      </listitem>

<!--
Author: Peter Eisentraut <peter@eisentraut.org>
2025-01-11 [ca87c415e] Add support for NOT ENFORCED in CHECK constraints
Author: Peter Eisentraut <peter@eisentraut.org>
2025-04-02 [eec0040c4] Add support for NOT ENFORCED in foreign key constraints
-->

      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=17229d77ba73c88f8ba49dc19919c6fb sig_cn_org=13d8e4bb992f49bb707e6ebc26d21b63 source=18.3 
      <para>
      Allow <link
      linkend="sql-createtable-parms-check"><literal>CHECK</literal></link>
      and <link linkend="sql-createtable-parms-references">foreign
      key</link> constraints to be specified as <literal>NOT
      ENFORCED</literal> (Amul Sul)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;ca87c415e">&sect;</ulink>
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;eec0040c4">&sect;</ulink>
      </para>
________________________________________________________-->
      <para>
      允许 <link
      linkend="sql-createtable-parms-check"><literal>CHECK</literal></link>
      和 <link linkend="sql-createtable-parms-references">外键</link> 约束被指定为 <literal>NOT
      ENFORCED</literal> (Amul Sul)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;ca87c415e">&sect;</ulink>
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;eec0040c4">&sect;</ulink>
      </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=17229d77ba73c88f8ba49dc19919c6fb -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=c3cfc6f6b60719b05114fb3dfcfc06b7 sig_cn_org=0b2bd043f8f8d896179d70077664b028 source=18.3 
      <para>
      This also adds column <link
      linkend="catalog-pg-constraint"><structname>pg_constraint</structname></link>.<structfield>conenforced</structfield>.
      </para>
________________________________________________________-->
      <para>
      这还添加了列 <link
      linkend="catalog-pg-constraint"><structname>pg_constraint</structname></link>.<structfield>conenforced</structfield>。
      </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=c3cfc6f6b60719b05114fb3dfcfc06b7 -->
      </listitem>

<!--
Author: Peter Eisentraut <peter@eisentraut.org>
2024-11-15 [9321d2fdf] Fix collation handling for foreign keys
-->

      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=6ecf39dde435fee631377169cb83da83 sig_cn_org=50445e6e9e10d4c86b5e6b320b9a0429 source=18.3 
      <para>
      Require <link
      linkend="sql-createtable-parms-references">primary/foreign key</link>
      relationships to use either deterministic collations or the the
      same nondeterministic collations (Peter Eisentraut)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;9321d2fdf">&sect;</ulink>
      </para>
________________________________________________________-->
      <para>
      要求 <link
      linkend="sql-createtable-parms-references">主/外键</link>
      关系使用确定性排序规则或相同的非确定性排序规则 (Peter Eisentraut)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;9321d2fdf">&sect;</ulink>
      </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=6ecf39dde435fee631377169cb83da83 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=4cce4bf0d6ca8c6867d1645f1a68acb9 sig_cn_org=f22cb2a8878cc6b2e804989b9f6e4be9 source=18.3 
      <para>
      The restore of a <xref linkend="app-pgdump"/>, also used by <xref
      linkend="pgupgrade"/>, will fail if these requirements are not met;
      schema changes must be made for these upgrade methods to succeed.
      </para>
________________________________________________________-->
      <para>
      如果不满足这些要求，<xref linkend="app-pgdump"/> 的恢复也会失败，
      该方法也被 <xref linkend="pgupgrade"/> 使用；
      必须进行模式更改以使这些升级方法成功。
      </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=4cce4bf0d6ca8c6867d1645f1a68acb9 -->
      </listitem>

<!--
Author: Álvaro Herrera <alvherre@alvh.no-ip.org>
2024-11-08 [14e87ffa5] Add pg_constraint rows for not-null constraints
Author: Fujii Masao <fujii@postgresql.org>
Branch: master Release: REL_18_BR [81ce602d4] 2025-06-26 20:25:34 +0900
-->

      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=02bacaad87bcb509b4f6ad1154f10f06 sig_cn_org=ec5220563142c38c1b6b447c370422bd source=18.3 
      <para>
      Store column <link
      linkend="sql-createtable-parms-not-null"><literal>NOT
      NULL</literal></link> specifications in <link
      linkend="catalog-pg-constraint"><structname>pg_constraint</structname></link>
      (Álvaro Herrera, Bernd Helmle)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;14e87ffa5">&sect;</ulink>
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;81ce602d4">&sect;</ulink>
      </para>
________________________________________________________-->
      <para>
      将列 <link
      linkend="sql-createtable-parms-not-null"><literal>NOT
      NULL</literal></link> 规范存储在 <link
      linkend="catalog-pg-constraint"><structname>pg_constraint</structname></link>
      (Álvaro Herrera, Bernd Helmle)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;14e87ffa5">&sect;</ulink>
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;81ce602d4">&sect;</ulink>
      </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=02bacaad87bcb509b4f6ad1154f10f06 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=e85a67765ec897a1fe24a1d2978f97ef sig_cn_org=4830a5d83ca39a70fd03f37ab9fdcf3c source=18.3 
      <para>
      This allows names to be specified for <literal>NOT NULL</literal>
      constraint.  This also adds <literal>NOT NULL</literal> constraints
      to foreign tables and <literal>NOT NULL</literal> inheritance
      control to local tables.
      </para>
________________________________________________________-->
      <para>
      这允许为 <literal>NOT NULL</literal> 约束指定名称。
      这还将 <literal>NOT NULL</literal> 约束添加到外部表，并将 <literal>NOT NULL</literal> 继承控制添加到本地表。
      </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=e85a67765ec897a1fe24a1d2978f97ef -->
      </listitem>

<!--
Author: Álvaro Herrera <alvherre@alvh.no-ip.org>
2025-04-07 [a379061a2] Allow NOT NULL constraints to be added as NOT VALID
-->

      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=a43626c1ef41900a3583bd257c6f54ba sig_cn_org=c66f3126b9e185fc1f5467cca722ff39 source=18.3 
      <para>
      Allow <xref linkend="sql-altertable"/> to set the <literal>NOT
      VALID</literal> attribute of <literal>NOT NULL</literal> constraints
      (Rushabh Lathia, Jian He)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;a379061a2">&sect;</ulink>
      </para>
________________________________________________________-->
      <para>
      允许 <xref linkend="sql-altertable"/> 设置 <literal>NOT
      VALID</literal> 属性的 <literal>NOT NULL</literal> 约束
      (Rushabh Lathia, Jian He)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;a379061a2">&sect;</ulink>
      </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=a43626c1ef41900a3583bd257c6f54ba -->
      </listitem>

<!--
Author: Álvaro Herrera <alvherre@alvh.no-ip.org>
2025-03-05 [f4e53e10b] Add ALTER TABLE ... ALTER CONSTRAINT ... SET [NO] INHERI
Author: Álvaro Herrera <alvherre@alvh.no-ip.org>
2025-03-27 [4a02af8b1] Simplify syntax for ALTER TABLE ALTER CONSTRAINT NO INHE
-->

      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=b3198313802a254b0e47acbcabc5a078 sig_cn_org=c6bfaf9ceb6add7d737c8ea2592a763d source=18.3 
      <para>
      Allow modification of the inheritability of <literal>NOT
      NULL</literal> constraints (Suraj Kharage, Álvaro Herrera)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;f4e53e10b">&sect;</ulink>
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;4a02af8b1">&sect;</ulink>
      </para>
________________________________________________________-->
      <para>
      允许修改 <literal>NOT NULL</literal> 约束的继承性 (Suraj Kharage, Álvaro Herrera)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;f4e53e10b">&sect;</ulink>
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;4a02af8b1">&sect;</ulink>
      </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=b3198313802a254b0e47acbcabc5a078 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=590783bc1ac49303739c566ce3c42995 sig_cn_org=7f934ff8b9df415b83d41a40b34e3bd6 source=18.3 
      <para>
      The syntax is <link linkend="sql-altertable"><command>ALTER TABLE
      ... ALTER CONSTRAINT ... [NO] INHERIT</command></link>.
      </para>
________________________________________________________-->
      <para>
      语法为 <link linkend="sql-altertable"><command>ALTER TABLE
      ... ALTER CONSTRAINT ... [NO] INHERIT</command></link>。
      </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=590783bc1ac49303739c566ce3c42995 -->
      </listitem>

<!--
Author: Álvaro Herrera <alvherre@alvh.no-ip.org>
2025-01-23 [b663b9436] Allow NOT VALID foreign key constraints on partitioned t
-->

      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=b52ab7195c13a0fc9bcbeeb3784a4a3f sig_cn_org=394e136e62adcc26255464dac0b88192 source=18.3 
      <para>
      Allow <literal>NOT VALID</literal> foreign key constraints on
      partitioned tables (Amul Sul)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;b663b9436">&sect;</ulink>
      </para>
________________________________________________________-->
      <para>
      允许在分区表上使用 <literal>NOT VALID</literal> 外键约束 (Amul Sul)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;b663b9436">&sect;</ulink>
      </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=b52ab7195c13a0fc9bcbeeb3784a4a3f -->
      </listitem>

<!--
Author: Álvaro Herrera <alvherre@alvh.no-ip.org>
2024-09-30 [4dea33ce7] Don't disallow DROP of constraints ONLY on partitioned t
-->

      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=d23d0447779269d5d40234ae721d8da6 sig_cn_org=44c3672619d2ca51bd59d3846830566d source=18.3 
      <para>
      Allow <link
      linkend="sql-altertable-desc-drop-constraint">dropping</link>
      of constraints <literal>ONLY</literal> on partitioned tables
      (Álvaro Herrera)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;4dea33ce7">&sect;</ulink>
      </para>
________________________________________________________-->
      <para>
      允许在分区表上<link
      linkend="sql-altertable-desc-drop-constraint">删除</link>
      约束 <literal>仅</literal> (Álvaro Herrera)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;4dea33ce7">&sect;</ulink>
      </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=d23d0447779269d5d40234ae721d8da6 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=34a31ca96f79229475aa1bf7e28c3329 sig_cn_org=e7dc8e945450839adcd137957b86ba2d source=18.3 
      <para>
      This was previously erroneously prohibited.
      </para>
________________________________________________________-->
      <para>
      之前错误地禁止了这一操作。
      </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=34a31ca96f79229475aa1bf7e28c3329 -->
      </listitem>

     </itemizedlist>
    </sect4>

    <sect4 id="release-18-copy">
     <title><xref linkend="sql-copy"/></title>

     <itemizedlist>

<!--
Author: Fujii Masao <fujii@postgresql.org>
2024-10-08 [4ac2a9bec] Add REJECT_LIMIT option to the COPY command.
-->

      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=1d9a4c775a4fb075b96405bfbf233887 sig_cn_org=1cb3467f6ef645f0051d2c737e0afd01 source=18.3 
      <para>
      Add <literal>REJECT_LIMIT</literal> to control the number of invalid
      rows <command>COPY FROM</command> can ignore (Atsushi Torikoshi)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;4ac2a9bec">&sect;</ulink>
      </para>
________________________________________________________-->
      <para>
      添加<literal>REJECT_LIMIT</literal>以控制<command>COPY FROM</command>
      可以忽略的无效行数 (Atsushi Torikoshi)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;4ac2a9bec">&sect;</ulink>
      </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=1d9a4c775a4fb075b96405bfbf233887 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=0fd15c3ba494a008ee7ec653f42daa22 sig_cn_org=56cf8333282b6c4372d41cde742e1023 source=18.3 
      <para>
      This is available when <literal>ON_ERROR = 'ignore'</literal>.
      </para>
________________________________________________________-->
      <para>
      当<literal>ON_ERROR = 'ignore'</literal>时可用。
      </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=0fd15c3ba494a008ee7ec653f42daa22 -->
      </listitem>

<!--
Author: Fujii Masao <fujii@postgresql.org>
2025-04-04 [534874fac] Allow "COPY table TO" command to copy rows from material
-->

      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=5b480b72cffe7fe8f557c46c8996dc2c sig_cn_org=e0b59d967b2623e979fb0d461910cc46 source=18.3 
      <para>
      Allow <command>COPY TO</command> to copy rows from populated
      materialized views (Jian He)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;534874fac">&sect;</ulink>
      </para>
________________________________________________________-->
      <para>
      允许<command>COPY TO</command>从已填充的物化视图中复制行
      (Jian He)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;534874fac">&sect;</ulink>
      </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=5b480b72cffe7fe8f557c46c8996dc2c -->
      </listitem>

<!--
Author: Fujii Masao <fujii@postgresql.org>
2024-10-03 [e7834a1a2] Add LOG_VERBOSITY = 'silent' support to COPY command.
-->

      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=081000882beb47c0a567286c0b567c7e sig_cn_org=055e29c6219fbdf23eee1ea7a6bcfe19 source=18.3 
      <para>
      Add <command>COPY</command> <literal>LOG_VERBOSITY</literal> level
      <literal>silent</literal> to suppress log output of ignored rows
      (Atsushi Torikoshi)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;e7834a1a2">&sect;</ulink>
      </para>
________________________________________________________-->
      <para>
      添加<command>COPY</command> <literal>LOG_VERBOSITY</literal>级别
      <literal>silent</literal>以抑制被忽略行的日志输出
      (Atsushi Torikoshi)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;e7834a1a2">&sect;</ulink>
      </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=081000882beb47c0a567286c0b567c7e -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=10e5fb378b235f5d471af3ccd274630e sig_cn_org=00785c33b165c1c6fa2e49de84a5f5de source=18.3 
      <para>
      This new level suppresses output for discarded input rows when
      <literal>on_error = 'ignore'</literal>.
      </para>
________________________________________________________-->
      <para>
      这个新级别在<literal>on_error = 'ignore'</literal>时抑制被丢弃的输入行的输出。
      </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=10e5fb378b235f5d471af3ccd274630e -->
      </listitem>

<!--
Author: Nathan Bossart <nathan@postgresql.org>
2025-02-06 [401a6956f] Disallow COPY FREEZE on foreign tables.
-->

      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=216359a8c870865ccf7405beb61b0784 sig_cn_org=0d063e71f7018b6e829684fc9930849c source=18.3 
      <para>
      Disallow <command>COPY FREEZE</command> on foreign tables (Nathan
      Bossart)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;401a6956f">&sect;</ulink>
      </para>
________________________________________________________-->
      <para>
      不允许在外部表上使用<command>COPY FREEZE</command> (Nathan
      Bossart)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;401a6956f">&sect;</ulink>
      </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=216359a8c870865ccf7405beb61b0784 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=53807d7054f3373fe1dea8ba8a34e68c sig_cn_org=98a01c9217096755c293b3e1ea4cafcf source=18.3 
      <para>
      Previously, the <command>COPY</command> worked but the
      <literal>FREEZE</literal> was ignored, so disallow this command.
      </para>
________________________________________________________-->
      <para>
      之前，<command>COPY</command>可以工作，但<literal>FREEZE</literal>被忽略，因此禁止此命令。
      </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=53807d7054f3373fe1dea8ba8a34e68c -->
      </listitem>

     </itemizedlist>
    </sect4>

