<!--
Author: Jeff Davis <jdavis@postgresql.org>
2025-01-24 [bfc599206] Add SQL function CASEFOLD().
-->

     <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=78b4356fb3da58ffc14064fc9ed787b7 sig_cn_org=72cc92b8743ce405912570aedad8d653 source=18.3 
     <para>
     Add function <link
     linkend="functions-string-other"><function>casefold()</function></link>
     to allow for more sophisticated case-insensitive matching (Jeff Davis)
     <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;bfc599206">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
     添加函数 <link
     linkend="functions-string-other"><function>casefold()</function></link>
     以允许更复杂的大小写不敏感匹配 (Jeff Davis)
     <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;bfc599206">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=78b4356fb3da58ffc14064fc9ed787b7 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=d8ff69b937aa637746d4947306c561d0 sig_cn_org=e4d0247001c414f30bc7a0a9d7c65214 source=18.3 
     <para>
     This allows more accurate comparisons, i.e., a character can have
     multiple upper or lower case equivalents, or upper or lower case
     conversion changes the number of characters.
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
     这允许更准确的比较，即，一个字符可以有多个
     大写或小写等价物，或者大写或小写转换会改变字符的数量。
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=d8ff69b937aa637746d4947306c561d0 -->
     </listitem>

<!--
Author: Tom Lane <tgl@sss.pgh.pa.us>
