2025-03-25 [1a759c832] psql: Make default \watch interval configurable
-->

     <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=a4bf33fe124efa8eed761fb2cc677a56 sig_cn_org=679437438da6a6f70cdeb5ccb5e090f7 source=18.3 
     <para>
     Add <application>psql</application> variable <xref
     linkend="app-psql-variables-watch-interval"/> to set the default <link
     linkend="app-psql-meta-command-watch"><literal>\watch</literal></link>
     wait time (Daniel Gustafsson)
     <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;1a759c832">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
     添加 <application>psql</application> 变量 <xref
     linkend="app-psql-variables-watch-interval"/> 以设置默认的 <link
     linkend="app-psql-meta-command-watch"><literal>\watch</literal></link>
     等待时间（Daniel Gustafsson）
     <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;1a759c832">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=a4bf33fe124efa8eed761fb2cc677a56 -->
     </listitem>

    </itemizedlist>

   </sect3>

   <sect3 id="release-18-server-apps">
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=1788929f4ef70ee9cb769ffde99cc0de sig_cn_org=None source=14.1 
    <title>Server Applications</title>
________________________________________________________-->
    <title>服务器应用</title>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=1788929f4ef70ee9cb769ffde99cc0de -->

    <itemizedlist>

<!--
Author: Peter Eisentraut <peter@eisentraut.org>
2024-10-01 [983a588e0] initdb: Add new option "- -no-data-checksums"
Author: Peter Eisentraut <peter@eisentraut.org>
2024-10-16 [04bec894a] initdb: Change default to using data checksums.
-->

     <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=00e7347d7a8450b21e751f45530a4b7b sig_cn_org=a2d2ec116f21c3985bad5d075085ef44 source=18.3 
     <para>
     Change <xref linkend="app-initdb"/> to default to enabling checksums
     (Greg Sabino Mullane)
     <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;983a588e0">&sect;</ulink>
     <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;04bec894a">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
     更改 <xref linkend="app-initdb"/> 的默认设置以启用校验和
     （Greg Sabino Mullane）
     <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;983a588e0">&sect;</ulink>
     <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;04bec894a">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=00e7347d7a8450b21e751f45530a4b7b -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=3640b5c76f639280e8df675e2320e262 sig_cn_org=9076fb0313b8d1fa1383d79d4b69288b source=18.3 
     <para>
     The new <application>initdb</application> option
     <option>-&minus;no-data-checksums</option> disables checksums.
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
     新的 <application>initdb</application> 选项
     <option>--no-data-checksums</option> 禁用校验和。
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=3640b5c76f639280e8df675e2320e262 -->
     </listitem>

<!--
Author: Nathan Bossart <nathan@postgresql.org>
2025-03-25 [cf131fa94] initdb: Add - -no-sync-data-files.
-->

     <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=ad0edb59a5c046f49cd5e03f345293c3 sig_cn_org=b4ce5850d8dcb28912a98165a595c569 source=18.3 
     <para>
     Add <application>initdb</application> option
     <option>-&minus;no-sync-data-files</option> to avoid syncing heap/index
     files (Nathan Bossart)
     <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;cf131fa94">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
     添加 <application>initdb</application> 选项
     <option>--no-sync-data-files</option> 以避免同步堆/索引
     文件（Nathan Bossart）
     <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;cf131fa94">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=ad0edb59a5c046f49cd5e03f345293c3 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=d32bc6aee9f5740524a6c3c058c7fdac sig_cn_org=64e84666e641d29104ddefc746de5b2d source=18.3 
     <para>
     <application>initdb</application> option <option>-&minus;no-sync</option>
     is still available to avoid syncing any files.
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
     <application>initdb</application> 选项 <option>--no-sync</option>
     仍然可用以避免同步任何文件。
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=d32bc6aee9f5740524a6c3c058c7fdac -->
     </listitem>

<!--
Author: Nathan Bossart <nathan@postgresql.org>
2025-03-18 [edba754f0] vacuumdb: Add option for analyzing only relations missin
Author: Nathan Bossart <nathan@postgresql.org>
2025-04-30 [987910502] vacuumdb: Don't skip empty relations in - -missing-stats-
-->

     <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=3182ea12c253429abfc4b38e7cc73bee sig_cn_org=f501ac13ebc7fbdd1516cac00db60090 source=18.3 
     <para>
     Add <xref linkend="app-vacuumdb"/> option
     <option>-&minus;missing-stats-only</option> to compute only missing
     optimizer statistics (Corey Huinker, Nathan Bossart)
     <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;edba754f0">&sect;</ulink>
     <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;987910502">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
     添加 <xref linkend="app-vacuumdb"/> 选项
     <option>--missing-stats-only</option> 仅计算缺失的
     优化器统计信息（Corey Huinker, Nathan Bossart）
     <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;edba754f0">&sect;</ulink>
     <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;987910502">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=3182ea12c253429abfc4b38e7cc73bee -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=db8a42ce780a36c7c50a02f33b01dfaf sig_cn_org=7d72fd0533f6cc6ce444ffbd412d0768 source=18.3 
     <para>
     This option can only be run by superusers and can only
     be used with options <option>-&minus;analyze-only</option> and
     <option>-&minus;analyze-in-stages</option>.
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
     此选项只能由超级用户运行，并且只能
     与选项 <option>--analyze-only</option> 和
     <option>--analyze-in-stages</option> 一起使用。
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=db8a42ce780a36c7c50a02f33b01dfaf -->
     </listitem>

<!--
Author: Robert Haas <rhaas@postgresql.org>
2025-03-17 [99aeb8470] pg_combinebackup: Add -k, - -link option.
-->

     <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=e785ae137ebd1f29f2251cff408e85ce sig_cn_org=63dc0629cff224a06614c830378cdaa3 source=18.3 
     <para>
     Add <xref linkend="app-pgcombinebackup"/> option
     <option>-k</option>/<option>-&minus;link</option> to enable hard linking
     (Israel Barth Rubio, Robert Haas)
     <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;99aeb8470">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
     添加 <xref linkend="app-pgcombinebackup"/> 选项
     <option>-k</option>/<option>--link</option> 以启用硬链接
     （Israel Barth Rubio, Robert Haas）
     <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;99aeb8470">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=e785ae137ebd1f29f2251cff408e85ce -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=26bf898d55a31322eba1fbb8303dbded sig_cn_org=0db9e94424212b22defba830229ec9b2 source=18.3 
     <para>
     Only some files can be hard linked.  This should not be used if the
     backups will be used independently.
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
     只有某些文件可以进行硬链接。如果备份将独立使用，则不应使用此功能。
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=26bf898d55a31322eba1fbb8303dbded -->
     </listitem>

<!--
Author: Robert Haas <rhaas@postgresql.org>
2024-09-27 [8dfd31290] pg_verifybackup: Verify tar-format backups.
-->

     <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=bc4a941c9ec608fdc7bbf413191a4373 sig_cn_org=64ba4cf4f57bad5630b15cd50c770f06 source=18.3 
     <para>
     Allow <xref linkend="app-pgverifybackup"/> to verify tar-format
     backups (Amul Sul)
     <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;8dfd31290">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
     允许 <xref linkend="app-pgverifybackup"/> 验证 tar 格式的备份（Amul Sul）
     <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;8dfd31290">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=bc4a941c9ec608fdc7bbf413191a4373 -->
     </listitem>

<!--
Author: Masahiko Sawada <msawada@postgresql.org>
2025-03-12 [4ecdd4110] pg_rewind: Add dbname to primary_conninfo when using - -w
-->

     <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=b41a725942da9c34ac1d6cb0f81740f4 sig_cn_org=457dd408a73b22d8b8daef42f4959f58 source=18.3 
     <para>
     If <xref linkend="app-pgrewind"/>'s <option>-&minus;source-server</option>
     specifies a database name, use it in
     <option>-&minus;write-recovery-conf</option> output (Masahiko Sawada)
     <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;4ecdd4110">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
     如果 <xref linkend="app-pgrewind"/>'s <option>--source-server</option>
     指定了数据库名称，则在 <option>--write-recovery-conf</option> 输出中使用它（Masahiko Sawada）
     <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;4ecdd4110">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=b41a725942da9c34ac1d6cb0f81740f4 -->
     </listitem>

<!--
Author: Masahiko Sawada <msawada@postgresql.org>
2025-02-21 [30666d185] pg_resetwal: Add - -char-signedness option to change the
-->

     <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=6176b7b286e5bc7e84bc8edf64e20b43 sig_cn_org=e314038b7d593a96e6b33fbf1d80664c source=18.3 
     <para>
     Add <xref linkend="app-pgresetwal"/> option
     <option>-&minus;char-signedness</option> to change the default
     <type>char</type> signedness (Masahiko Sawada)
     <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;30666d185">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
     添加 <xref linkend="app-pgresetwal"/> 选项 <option>--char-signedness</option> 以更改默认的 <type>char</type> 符号性（Masahiko Sawada）
     <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;30666d185">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=6176b7b286e5bc7e84bc8edf64e20b43 -->
     </listitem>

    </itemizedlist>


    <sect4 id="release-18-pgdump">
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=73a19c398c60fad862f35cd0ed92a9e4 sig_cn_org=ca2e86413b9c1b7c86894e09f9b71549 source=18.3 
     <title><link
     linkend="app-pgdump"><application>pg_dump</application></link>/<link
     linkend="app-pg-dumpall"><application>pg_dumpall</application></link>/<link
     linkend="app-pgrestore"><application>pg_restore</application></link></title>
________________________________________________________-->
     <title><link
     linkend="app-pgdump"><application>pg_dump</application></link>/<link
     linkend="app-pg-dumpall"><application>pg_dumpall</application></link>/<link
     linkend="app-pgrestore"><application>pg_restore</application></link></title>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=73a19c398c60fad862f35cd0ed92a9e4 -->

     <itemizedlist>

<!--
Author: Jeff Davis <jdavis@postgresql.org>
2025-03-25 [bde2fb797] Add pg_dump - -with-{schema|data|statistics} options.
Author: Jeff Davis <jdavis@postgresql.org>
2025-08-02 [a3e8dc143] Simplify options in pg_dump and pg_restore.
-->

      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=2bbdeb7abf4e92bb0f147383cdacda36 sig_cn_org=aa088c1a6d9b1e81dd249e62af07fdaf source=18.3 
      <para>
      Add <xref linkend="app-pgdump"/> option <option>-&minus;statistics</option>
      (Jeff Davis)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;bde2fb797">&sect;</ulink>
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;a3e8dc143">&sect;</ulink>
      </para>
________________________________________________________-->
      <para>
      添加 <xref linkend="app-pgdump"/> 选项 <option>--statistics</option>（Jeff Davis）
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;bde2fb797">&sect;</ulink>
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;a3e8dc143">&sect;</ulink>
      </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=2bbdeb7abf4e92bb0f147383cdacda36 -->
      </listitem>

<!--
Author: Nathan Bossart <nathan@postgresql.org>
2025-03-25 [9c49f0e8c] pg_dump: Add - -sequence-data.
Author: Nathan Bossart <nathan@postgresql.org>
2025-05-07 [acea3fc49] pg_dumpall: Add - -sequence-data.
-->

      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=c9bdd8aca01058d968df3ec84c7e32fa sig_cn_org=328968ecfc9f8cf3a011f8f982ca7b53 source=18.3 
      <para>
      Add <application>pg_dump</application> and <xref
      linkend="app-pg-dumpall"/> option <option>-&minus;sequence-data</option> to
      dump sequence data that would normally be excluded (Nathan Bossart)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;9c49f0e8c">&sect;</ulink>
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;acea3fc49">&sect;</ulink>
      </para>
________________________________________________________-->
      <para>
      添加 <application>pg_dump</application> 和 <xref
      linkend="app-pg-dumpall"/> 选项 <option>--sequence-data</option> 以转储通常会被排除的序列数据（Nathan Bossart）
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;9c49f0e8c">&sect;</ulink>
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;acea3fc49">&sect;</ulink>
      </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=c9bdd8aca01058d968df3ec84c7e32fa -->
      </listitem>

<!--
Author: Jeff Davis <jdavis@postgresql.org>
2025-02-20 [1fd1bd871] Transfer statistics during pg_upgrade.
-->

      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=1107506d0983c61ff6ef26498dde4675 sig_cn_org=c3b7fd2beffe10f7a2284287175097f8 source=18.3 
      <para>
      Add <xref linkend="app-pgdump"/>, <xref linkend="app-pg-dumpall"/>,
      and <xref linkend="app-pgrestore"/> options
      <option>-&minus;statistics-only</option>, <option>-&minus;no-statistics</option>,
      <option>-&minus;no-data</option>, and <option>-&minus;no-schema</option>
      (Corey Huinker, Jeff Davis)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;1fd1bd871">&sect;</ulink>
      </para>
________________________________________________________-->
      <para>
      添加 <xref linkend="app-pgdump"/>, <xref linkend="app-pg-dumpall"/>,
      和 <xref linkend="app-pgrestore"/> 选项
      <option>--statistics-only</option>, <option>--no-statistics</option>,
      <option>--no-data</option>, 和 <option>--no-schema</option>
      （Corey Huinker, Jeff Davis）
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;1fd1bd871">&sect;</ulink>
      </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=1107506d0983c61ff6ef26498dde4675 -->
      </listitem>

<!--
Author: Tom Lane <tgl@sss.pgh.pa.us>
2025-03-16 [cd3c45125] pg_dump, pg_dumpall, pg_restore: Add - -no-policies optio
-->

      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=509fa5eb94a513c375c9740377e04ccf sig_cn_org=1e73389abae22c805809035068cafcbf source=18.3 
      <para>
      Add option <option>-&minus;no-policies</option> to disable row level
      security policy processing in <xref linkend="app-pgdump"/>,
      <xref linkend="app-pg-dumpall"/>, <xref linkend="app-pgrestore"/>
      (Nikolay Samokhvalov)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;cd3c45125">&sect;</ulink>
      </para>
________________________________________________________-->
      <para>
      添加选项 <option>--no-policies</option> 以禁用 <xref linkend="app-pgdump"/>,
      <xref linkend="app-pg-dumpall"/>, <xref linkend="app-pgrestore"/> 中的行级安全策略处理
      （Nikolay Samokhvalov）
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;cd3c45125">&sect;</ulink>
      </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=509fa5eb94a513c375c9740377e04ccf -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=a7dc37d76d830a5ca9187e5086055e90 sig_cn_org=df4fe0445429bd4d3b81257fd1a75fe1 source=18.3 
      <para>
      This is useful for migrating to systems with different policies.
      </para>
________________________________________________________-->
      <para>
      这对于迁移到具有不同策略的系统非常有用。
      </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=a7dc37d76d830a5ca9187e5086055e90 -->
      </listitem>

     </itemizedlist>

    </sect4>

    <sect4 id="release-18-pgupgrade">
     <title><xref linkend="pgupgrade"/></title>

     <itemizedlist>

<!--
Author: Jeff Davis <jdavis@postgresql.org>
2025-02-20 [1fd1bd871] Transfer statistics during pg_upgrade.
Author: Nathan Bossart <nathan@postgresql.org>
2025-03-18 [c9d502eb6] Update guidance for running vacuumdb after pg_upgrade.
Author: Nathan Bossart <nathan@postgresql.org>
2025-04-30 [d5f1b6a75] Further adjust guidance for running vacuumdb after pg_up
Author: Jeff Davis <jdavis@postgresql.org>
2025-02-20 [1fd1bd871] Transfer statistics during pg_upgrade.
-->

      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=1e61bbaaf28f5af2ea53abff79b18647 sig_cn_org=35cdfe498402ec4f64099943f712676a source=18.3 
      <para>
      Allow <application>pg_upgrade</application> to preserve optimizer
      statistics (Corey Huinker, Jeff Davis, Nathan Bossart)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;1fd1bd871">&sect;</ulink>
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;c9d502eb6">&sect;</ulink>
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;d5f1b6a75">&sect;</ulink>
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;1fd1bd871">&sect;</ulink>
      </para>
________________________________________________________-->
      <para>
      允许 <application>pg_upgrade</application> 保留优化器统计信息（Corey Huinker, Jeff Davis, Nathan Bossart）
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;1fd1bd871">&sect;</ulink>
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;c9d502eb6">&sect;</ulink>
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;d5f1b6a75">&sect;</ulink>
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;1fd1bd871">&sect;</ulink>
      </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=1e61bbaaf28f5af2ea53abff79b18647 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=eca5573211e50fce3ef174a93eea87da sig_cn_org=58b81332c49be212b9e023140449690d source=18.3 
      <para>
      Extended statistics are not preserved.  Also add
      <application>pg_upgrade</application> option
      <option>-&minus;no-statistics</option> to disable statistics preservation.
      </para>
________________________________________________________-->
      <para>
      扩展统计信息不会被保留。还添加 <application>pg_upgrade</application> 选项
      <option>--no-statistics</option> 以禁用统计信息的保留。
      </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=eca5573211e50fce3ef174a93eea87da -->
      </listitem>

<!--
Author: Nathan Bossart <nathan@postgresql.org>
2024-09-16 [40e2e5e92] Introduce framework for parallelizing various pg_upgrade
Author: Nathan Bossart <nathan@postgresql.org>
2024-09-16 [6d3d2e8e5] pg_upgrade: Parallelize retrieving relation information.
Author: Nathan Bossart <nathan@postgresql.org>
2024-09-16 [7baa36de5] pg_upgrade: Parallelize subscription check.
Author: Nathan Bossart <nathan@postgresql.org>
2024-09-16 [46cad8b31] pg_upgrade: Parallelize retrieving loadable libraries.
Author: Nathan Bossart <nathan@postgresql.org>
2024-09-16 [6ab8f27bc] pg_upgrade: Parallelize retrieving extension updates.
Author: Nathan Bossart <nathan@postgresql.org>
2024-09-16 [bbf83cab9] pg_upgrade: Parallelize data type checks.
Author: Nathan Bossart <nathan@postgresql.org>
2024-09-16 [9db3018cf] pg_upgrade: Parallelize contrib/isn check.
Author: Nathan Bossart <nathan@postgresql.org>
2024-09-16 [c34eabfbb] pg_upgrade: Parallelize postfix operator check.
Author: Nathan Bossart <nathan@postgresql.org>
2024-09-16 [cf2f82a37] pg_upgrade: Parallelize incompatible polymorphics check.
Author: Nathan Bossart <nathan@postgresql.org>
2024-09-16 [f93f5f7b9] pg_upgrade: Parallelize WITH OIDS check.
Author: Nathan Bossart <nathan@postgresql.org>
2024-09-16 [c880cf258] pg_upgrade: Parallelize encoding conversion check.
-->

      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=6d710c8c3653d828490a007a1f132b29 sig_cn_org=ca9a8332862b8a2f6fcc57447da95ca4 source=18.3 
      <para>
      Allow <application>pg_upgrade</application> to process database
      checks in parallel (Nathan Bossart)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;40e2e5e92">&sect;</ulink>
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;6d3d2e8e5">&sect;</ulink>
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;7baa36de5">&sect;</ulink>
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;46cad8b31">&sect;</ulink>
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;6ab8f27bc">&sect;</ulink>
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;bbf83cab9">&sect;</ulink>
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;9db3018cf">&sect;</ulink>
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;c34eabfbb">&sect;</ulink>
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;cf2f82a37">&sect;</ulink>
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;f93f5f7b9">&sect;</ulink>
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;c880cf258">&sect;</ulink>
      </para>
________________________________________________________-->
      <para>
      允许 <application>pg_upgrade</application> 并行处理数据库检查（Nathan Bossart）
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;40e2e5e92">&sect;</ulink>
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;6d3d2e8e5">&sect;</ulink>
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;7baa36de5">&sect;</ulink>
