Author: Amit Kapila <akapila@postgresql.org>
2025-02-26 [e117cfb2f] Add two-phase option in pg_createsubscriber.
-->

      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=0f98aad430e46c15d4a468a8b44302e0 sig_cn_org=d2f58e5cc66c0dab16c0e1a15118b526 source=18.3 
