Author: Masahiko Sawada <msawada@postgresql.org>
2025-04-04 [cf2655a90] pg_recvlogical: Add - -failover option.
-->

      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=3b1415b3e475c9e75b94fb1c07b804bf sig_cn_org=bbec32f91c7dc17440cc6e8432a123b2 source=18.3 
