<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=cdb3d418b6cf60e5a53730615151cc1c sig_cn_org=7a526959a898fdd2342c477775381c9f source=18.3 
     <para>
     Add output columns to <link
     linkend="postgres-fdw-functions"><function>postgres_fdw_get_connections()</function></link>
     (Hayato Kuroda, Sagar Dilip Shedge)
     <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;c297a47c5">&sect;</ulink>
     <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;857df3cef">&sect;</ulink>
     <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;4f08ab554">&sect;</ulink>
     <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;fe186bda7">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
     向 <link
     linkend="postgres-fdw-functions"><function>postgres_fdw_get_connections()</function></link>
     添加输出列 (Hayato Kuroda, Sagar Dilip Shedge)
     <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;c297a47c5">&sect;</ulink>
     <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;857df3cef">&sect;</ulink>
     <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;4f08ab554">&sect;</ulink>
     <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;fe186bda7">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=cdb3d418b6cf60e5a53730615151cc1c -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=c25373f57f211b30e242938332eaf06e sig_cn_org=f2b7d7493534e140c4f7ebc850ffb130 source=18.3 
     <para>
     New output column <structfield>used_in_xact</structfield> indicates
     if the foreign data wrapper is being used by a current transaction,
     <structfield>closed</structfield> indicates if it is closed,
     <structfield>user_name</structfield> indicates the user name, and
     <structfield>remote_backend_pid</structfield> indicates the remote
     backend process identifier.
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
     新输出列 <structfield>used_in_xact</structfield> 指示
     外部数据包装器是否被当前事务使用，
     <structfield>closed</structfield> 指示它是否已关闭，
     <structfield>user_name</structfield> 指示用户名，以及
     <structfield>remote_backend_pid</structfield> 指示远程
     后端进程标识符。
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=c25373f57f211b30e242938332eaf06e -->
     </listitem>

<!--
Author: Peter Eisentraut <peter@eisentraut.org>
2025-01-15 [761c79508] postgres_fdw: SCRAM authentication pass-through
-->

     <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=5433a467cc06e51aa7ab9d0d023ea202 sig_cn_org=3421c0abffffebde88ec2dc1d9038850 source=18.3 
     <para>
     Allow <link linkend="auth-password"><acronym>SCRAM</acronym></link>
     authentication from the client to be passed to <xref
     linkend="postgres-fdw"/> servers (Matheus Alcantara, Peter Eisentraut)
     <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;761c79508">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
     允许从客户端传递 <link linkend="auth-password"><acronym>SCRAM</acronym></link>
     认证到 <xref
     linkend="postgres-fdw"/> 服务器 (Matheus Alcantara, Peter Eisentraut)
     <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;761c79508">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=5433a467cc06e51aa7ab9d0d023ea202 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=88e258f82376a77b9dc1609ad9eb11ee sig_cn_org=850d06a4c81f84098e4cf0870542a544 source=18.3 
     <para>
     This avoids storing <application>postgres_fdw</application>
     authentication information in the database, and is
     enabled with the <application>postgres_fdw</application> <link
     linkend="postgres-fdw-option-use-scram-passthrough"><literal>use_scram_passthrough</literal></link>
     connection option.  libpq uses new connection parameters
     <xref linkend="libpq-connect-scram-client-key"/> and <xref
     linkend="libpq-connect-scram-server-key"/>.
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
     这避免了将 <application>postgres_fdw</application>
     身份验证信息存储在数据库中，并通过 <application>postgres_fdw</application> 
     <link linkend="postgres-fdw-option-use-scram-passthrough"><literal>use_scram_passthrough</literal></link>
     连接选项启用。 libpq 使用新的连接参数
     <xref linkend="libpq-connect-scram-client-key"/> 和 <xref
     linkend="libpq-connect-scram-server-key"/>。
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=88e258f82376a77b9dc1609ad9eb11ee -->
     </listitem>

<!--
Author: Peter Eisentraut <peter@eisentraut.org>
2025-03-26 [3642df265] dblink: SCRAM authentication pass-through
-->

     <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=56d72ccfb466c1bbd80e2f9a2087e2a4 sig_cn_org=9c2033d68d4c376dd0809cb1860d53bb source=18.3 
     <para>
     Allow <acronym>SCRAM</acronym> authentication from the client to be
     passed to <xref linkend="dblink"/> servers (Matheus Alcantara)
     <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;3642df265">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
     允许从客户端传递 <acronym>SCRAM</acronym> 身份验证到 
     <xref linkend="dblink"/> 服务器 (Matheus Alcantara)
     <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;3642df265">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=56d72ccfb466c1bbd80e2f9a2087e2a4 -->
     </listitem>

